  "description": "<p>\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i1.s.hjfile.cn/entry/201303/9dba95e6-25b3-4e7f-90d1-6468fc4defa2.jpg\" style=\"height: 436px; width: 400px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p718259\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tBut first today Switzerland is a country which prides itself on direct <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/democracy\" target=\"_blank\">democracy</a>, a country where many crucial issues are put to a straight public vote - a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/referendum\" target=\"_blank\">referendum</a>. Well the latest <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/plebiscite\" target=\"_blank\">plebiscite</a> has seen Swiss voters giving their overwhelming backing to <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/curb\" target=\"_blank\">curbs</a> on corporate salaries, bonuses and golden handshakes. I wonder how many people would vote for a system like Switzerland's right now, probably not many execs. But roughly 68% of all those who voted in Switzerland supported the so-called Minder initiative or Rip-off initiative, as it's been called. All of Switzerland's 26 cantons were in favour. And basically what it does is give the control of executive pay back to the shareholders of individual companies. They will decide in future who gets what. Well Brigitta Moser-Harder is an active shareholder and member of the committee of the Swiss popular <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/initiative\" target=\"_blank\">initiative</a> against abusive executive compensation.</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;Well the public support was wonderful. You know, we started this initiative in 2006. And from the beginning we had so much support. Also when we collected the signatures, people helped us <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/spontaneously\" target=\"_blank\">spontaneously</a>. And in 2008 we already could give to the government and the parliament over 100,000 signatures.&quot;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(128,128,128); line-height: 25px;\">声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a class=\"creatLinks\" href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/tag/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-family: verdana, arial; border-bottom: rgb(0,90,148) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,90,148); line-height: 25px;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"更多英语内容\">英语</a><span style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(128,128,128); line-height: 25px;\">&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p718259/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p718259\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p718853/\">看我大中华料理如何完爆英国年度早餐</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p718749/\">冷风刮成表情帝 英女王冒严寒守岁</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p718767/\">囧囧英语 这些Chinglish你说过吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p718702/\">放价补脑，节后超diao！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p719008/\">一道小学生算术题难倒了首相卡梅伦</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p719179/\">台湾客机坠毁 16名大陆游客遇难</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p719059/\">殚精竭虑 一生只写一部著作的巨匠</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 